snippet.title: PlayStation All-Stars Battle Royale Fearless Stage DLC Gameplay
snippet.description:
Superbot Entertainment released some new DLC today for PlayStation All-Stars Battle Royale that adds Kat and Emmett Graves to the character roster along with a new Wipeout/Heavenly Sword crossover stage!
